short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirect from Go source code repositories(ex. Github) to official documentation

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Many time Go developers fail to mention official documentation URL for their repository. We have to manually go to the pkg.go.dev and search for that repository. This extension helps to go to the documentation right from the repository.
